<item>
            <title>[LU-10883] llog backup files processing is not skipped because of string &#1089;omparison error</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10883</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Buggy code was introduced in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7160&quot; title=&quot;Saved by change_nids .bak files on MGS should never be processed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7160&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-7160&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; fix&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;		&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;/* filter out &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;.bak&quot;&lt;/span&gt; files */&lt;/span&gt;
		&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;/* sizeof(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;.bak&quot;&lt;/span&gt;) - 1 == 3 */&lt;/span&gt;
		&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (key_sz &amp;gt;= 3 &amp;amp;&amp;amp;
		    !memcmp(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;.bak&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, key + key_sz - 3, 3)) {
			CDEBUG(D_MGS, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Skipping backup file %.*s\n&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,
			       key_sz, key);
			&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;goto&lt;/span&gt; next;
		}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;4 last key&apos;s bytes need to be compared with &quot;.bak&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
